1
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:27,720
I didn't expect Yin Zixi to be this kind of person.

2
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:28,920
Actually, it's not surprising.

3
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:30,280
For her to be so successful,

4
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:33,140
there must be something going on behind the scenes.

5
00:00:38,480 --> 00:00:39,840
Wen Lingli.

6
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:41,840
Liang Chen,

7
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:44,000
come out with me for a moment.

8
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:46,320
Oh.

9
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,200
Liang Chen,

10
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:57,240
why did you bring me here?

11
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,600
Because there are some things

12
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:01,130
I don't want others to know.

13
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:12,840
You took this photo, didn't you?

14
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:15,360
It's Yin Zixi again.

15
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:22,080
Just name your price.

16
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:23,840
Money is not a problem.

17
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,770
Don't come over!

18
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,400
So what if it was me?

19
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:30,680
I just happened to pass by that day.

20
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:32,080
Just happened to pass by?

21
00:01:32,759 --> 00:01:34,020
What about the rumors?

22
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,620
Did you start them too?

23
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:39,120
I just wanted to expose her true colors.

24
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,479
Liang Chen,

25
00:01:40,479 --> 00:01:42,880
how can you still not see it clearly?

26
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:50,120
The consequences of spreading rumors are very serious.

27
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,840
Your dad asked me to look after you.

28
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,920
I have the right and duty to remind you.

29
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,250
I didn't spread rumors.

30
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,400
She deserved it.

31
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,880
Whether you spread rumors or not,

32
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:02,240
we'll know once I find those two thugs.

33
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,000
Lili.

34
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:08,639
If you really did it,

35
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:11,480
I hope you go to the school voluntarily.

36
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,800
And confess.

37
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:37,360
Hey, who are you looking for?

38
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:40,090
Hey, what are you doing?

39
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:49,360
This guy is a former employee of your internet cafe, right?

40
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,160
I think so.

41
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,079
What's wrong?

42
00:02:52,079 --> 00:02:55,280
He harassed female students and spread rumors in school.

43
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:59,000
No way. Who would dare to come here after this?

44
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:03,080
Let me know immediately if you have any news about these two.

45
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:03,800
Okay.

46
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,600
Thanks.

47
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:21,800
What bad luck.

48
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,400
Not only did I get beaten up,

49
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,160
now I've even lost my job.

50
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:26,760
Let's go ask that woman for money.

51
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:27,520
Let's go.

52
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:29,880
Ouch.

53
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:41,770
How much do you think we should ask her for?

54
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:45,079
Definitely not the same amount as before.

55
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:52,720
What if she refuses?

56
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:55,380
I'll threaten her with the evidence.

57
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:01,130
There are so many mosquitoes here.

58
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,520
This is the place.

59
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,400
It's you.

60
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,680
Let go.

61
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,800
You are the mastermind behind this.

62
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,360
I think you are.

63
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:30,760
Tell me,

64
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,280
why did you spread rumors?

65
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:32,960
I didn't.

66
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,290
What did you say?

67
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:36,240
Fifty thousand?

68
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:38,320
You're asking for an exorbitant price.

69
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,560
Keep your voice down.

70
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:42,080
This is too much.

71
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,720
We agreed on 5,000 before.

72
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,520
Now you suddenly want 50,000.

73
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,720
I can't pay that.

74
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,320
Because of you, we two brothers

75
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:49,560
can't stay here anymore.

76
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,920
Isn't that perfect

77
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,760
for you to leave here?

78
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,120
What do you mean perfect?

79
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:54,920
If it weren't for your business,

80
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,920
Yin Zixi,

81
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,080
we wouldn't be leaving.

82
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,360
Why is she here?

83
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,480
Be quiet.

84
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,160
The previous 5,000

85
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,400
was the acting fee.

86
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,760
Now we are injured

87
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,760
and lost our jobs.

88
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,840
This 50,000 is for medical bills and lost wages.

89
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:11,560
If you don't pay,

90
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,640
don't blame us.

91
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,960
I will hand the evidence over to your school.

92
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,480
You wouldn't want to drop out of

93
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,610
a perfectly good university halfway.

94
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,480
Yin Zixi!

95
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,770
You secretly filmed me.

96
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:31,160
Stop!

97
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:35,360
Lili.

98
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:38,000
Brother Liang Chen.

99
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,320
Did you really do it?

100
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,200
Did you order the kidnapping too?

101
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:45,600
Do you know how much damage this has caused?

102
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,600
If you really did it,

103
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:50,440
I hope you take the initiative to confess to the school.

104
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:51,570
I will plead for you.

105
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:52,880
Confess?

106
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:55,000
Why should I confess?

107
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,080
Dream on.

108
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:02,320
Don't chase her.

109
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,960
She has my phone.

110
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,290
There's evidence on it.

111
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,130
There's one over there too.

112
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,520
Strange.

113
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,480
What's wrong?

114
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,760
Your phone.

115
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,880
Thank you.

116
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:26,120
When I chased her out just now,

117
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,200
she threw the phone away.

118
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,320
By the time I found it,

119
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:30,000
it wouldn't turn on.

120
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,680
I'll take it to be repaired

121
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,610
to see if the data can be recovered.

122
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,360
What if it can't be restored?

123
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:37,200
It's fine.

124
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:38,480
I still have the surveillance video.

125
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,560
Senior, how is it?

126
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:43,680
The camera is not connected to the internet.

127
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,880
So there's no record then.

128
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,920
I need to check.

129
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,440
Ah.

130
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,840
If you hadn't stopped me earlier,

131
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:52,960
I would have come in and taken those guys

132
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:53,480
down.

133
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,480
Then there wouldn't have been so much trouble later.

134
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,360
Really?

135
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,360
If you're so tough,

136
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,420
how come you can't even outrun a girl?

137
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:01,560
That's because there was a big uphill.

138
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,560
Why didn't you go?

139
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,440
Because I think too highly of you.

140
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,200
Okay.

141
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,240
Come on.

142
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:09,500
You were the one who ambushed me just now.

143
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,320
Are you sure?

144
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,720
Of course I'm sure.

145
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:14,560
Zixi.

146
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,420
Be the referee.

147
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:22,300
Good thing there's a memory card.

148
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,780
Are you done fighting?

149
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:27,080
Who won?

150
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:37,280
You said it was just an act to scare her.

151
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:38,920
Now that you've made such a big mess,

152
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,120
what should we do?

153
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,640
How about

154
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:43,880
you guys find a place to lay low first?

155
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,400
After we leave,

156
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:46,960
you'll be living comfortably.

157
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,360
Then what do you say we do?

158
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:50,440
They've already tracked it down to you.

159
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,240
You can't expect

160
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:53,320
to drag me into this too.

161
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,360
Plus medical and lost wage expenses,

162
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,960
add another fifty thousand.

163
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,360
I really didn't expect

164
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:03,090
that Wen Lingli was the one spreading this rumor.

165
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,580
Zixi, don't worry.

166
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,080
Our school

167
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:08,280
will definitely clarify the truth of this matter

168
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,610
and get justice for you.

169
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:10,940
Thank you, sir.

170
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,680
Sir,

171
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,440
we won't disturb you any longer.

172
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,370
Yeah, head back.

173
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,160
Goodbye, sir.

174
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,440
Okay, go ahead.

175
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:22,520
Sir.

176
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,440
Liang Chen,

177
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,050
is there anything else?

178
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:28,320
I would like to ask

179
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:31,530
what will be the final punishment for Wen Lingli?

180
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:34,130
You don't need to worry about this.

181
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:37,240
Besides, we won't know until the school committee discusses it.

182
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,039
I will take this

183
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,320
to the principal first.

184
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:39,880
Okay.

185
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,720
I am sorry.

186
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:52,480
The rumor incident this time

187
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,920
was all because of me,

188
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,330
causing a negative impact on society,

189
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,600
damaging the school's reputation,

190
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,840
and hurting everyone's feelings.

191
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,000
Especially,

192
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,480
especially to Yin Zixi,

193
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,560
the personal harm.

194
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:07,720
I am sorry.

195
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:14,480
As for the result of handling this matter,

196
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,520
our school

197
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:16,880
will have an internal discussion

198
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,340
and make a final decision.

199
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:19,600
Given

200
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,040
the impact of this matter on our students

201
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:21,880
personally,

202
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,760
I have already notified

203
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:24,920
the parents of both parties,

204
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:25,720
and they will arrive at noon.

205
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:26,800
I hope you students

206
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:28,040
can also learn a lesson

207
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:29,320
from this incident.

208
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,440
Parents?

209
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,820
I'm glad you're at the apartment.

210
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:39,760
When are you going to get your phone fixed?

211
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:40,920
Later.

212
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:44,280
I want to move the equipment back to the streaming room first.

213
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,440
What's wrong?

214
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:47,240
My parents are coming.

215
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,680
Xixi.

216
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:53,120
Dad.

217
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,080
Mom.

218
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,480
Casting Director Xi Chongjing

219
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:11,400
Props Assistant Li Kunxiao

220
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,400
Production Assistants: Che Yimingle,

221
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:15,320
Yitong.
